{"tid":2346840,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"不服來辯 落cream 仲叫唔叫卡邦尼意粉","createTime":"2020-12-30T14:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T15:22:37.000Z","uid":31414,"like":20,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"69c195c229c5b4d7de35a5e3ad9875a1a432dcbd","tid":2346840,"uid":31414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"近日見到有巴打講開呢個問題，雖然一定唔叫正宗，因為係意大利落cream 既芝士煙肉意粉叫 alfredo，所以一定唔會係正宗，但呢家世界各地有咁多人唔同做法，味道可能都有驚喜。所以細佬我都分享下自己做法，係小弟歐洲讀書時一個做廚師既朋友教我（係佢身上學fine dinning上碟多最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4CFnRKCZ65A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4CFnRKCZ65A&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=f19450b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4CFnRKCZ65A</a><br />\n後尾因為懶洗碗研究d 懶人做法（不是正宗），等係屋企heahea 地都可以食好d，又唔洗點洗碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />～～～<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qc9pRw5YrAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fqc9pRw5YrAA&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=c985169c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qc9pRw5YrAA</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家多多支持小弟，係屋企都享受到出面Fine Dining嘅味道，希望大家可以LIKE SUBSCRIBE 同SHARE，一齊對抗GAYGAYCOOK呢D藍廢Channel 。<br />\nMeWe: <a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/billylaws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2Fbillylaws&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=22fff633\" target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/billylaws</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/billylaws_hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbillylaws_hk%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=ba1509e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/billylaws_hk/</a><br />\nYoutube channel: BillyLaws 比利羅氏: <a